name: Seattle, WA
description: Data.Seattle.Gov provides access to datasets provided by various departments of Seattle City Government, including the City Budget Office, Seattle Fire Department, Department of Transportation, and many more. Data.Seattle.Gov uses the Socrata Open Data API, which uses the REST protocol.
